## Title 
### Underwater Hydraulic Power Unit
### Sous-marins Unités de Puissance Hydraulique
#### Tender Reference
##### cb-5814-2512334
 
## Tender Information
### Date of Publication
The Underwater Hydraulic Power Unit tender was published on May 25, 2023.
### Closing Date
The closing date for the tender is July 24, 2023 at 14:00:00.
 
## Contract Details
### Solicitation Number
W8476-226528/B
### Amendment Number
7
### Amendment Date
July 24, 2023
### Tender Status
Expired
 
## Procurement Information
### Procurement Category
Goods and Services (GD)
### Procurement Method
Competitive – Open Bidding
### Notice Type
Request for Proposal (RFP)
### Selection Criteria
Lowest Price
 
## Trade Agreements
Canada-Honduras Free Trade Agreement
Canadian Free Trade Agreement (CFTA)
Canada-Colombia Free Trade Agreement
Canada-Panama Free Trade Agreement
Canada-Korea Free Trade Agreement (CKFTA)
Canada-Chile Free Trade Agreement (CCFTA)
 
## Tender Description
The Department of National Defence (DND) requires 11 Underwater Hydraulic Power Units and Integrated Logistics Support (ILS) deliverables for delivery to Canadian Forces Supply Depot (CFSD) Montreal, Quebec. The requested delivery date is 120 days after contract award.
 
## Requirements
Delivery locations, quantities required, mandatory requirements, and deliverables information are detailed in Annex A: Requirement, and Annex B: Basis of Payment, of this solicitation package.
 
## Languages
Documents may be submitted in either official language of Canada.
 
## Contact Information
